article_title: Israel tells Palestinians to leave parts of eastern Rafah.
sentence: He  said  the  operation  was  part  of  the  endeavour  to  dismantle  Hamas  saying  that  it  had  shown  its  ability  to  launch  attacks  from  the  city  by  firing  rockets  from  Rafah  yesterday,  killing  three  Israeli  soldiers  near  the  Kerem  Shalom  crossing.
